CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 24, 1959, pg. 2 reads: "Seek Justice - Mrs. Anne Phillips and A.E.Evans, both of the 5200 b[l]ock of Broad St., niece and brother, respectively, of 80-year-old murder victim Green Evans, are shown in court this week as they looked forward with hope that justice would be dealt to 19-year-old Walter Joseph Phillips, who admitted the slaying.-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Anne Phillips, niece and A.E.Evans, brother of murder victim Green Evans, standing in corridor of the Allegheny County Courthouse
